# Weather App

A React Weather App that allows users to get the current weather and 5-day forecast for any city or their current location using OpenWeather API.

## Features

- Search weather by city name
- Get weather based on your current location
- Display current temperature, description, and weather icon
- Show 5-day weather forecast
- Error handling for invalid city or location issues

## Technologies Used

- React
- Axios (for API requests)
- OpenWeather API
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript

